  <div>
    <p>
A 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_nurse_clinic">Nurse Clinic</xref>
 is a 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_clinic_or_facility">CLINIC OR FACILITY</xref>.        </p>
    <p>
A 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_nurse_clinic">Nurse Clinic</xref>
Â is an 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_out-patient_clinic">Out-Patient Clinic</xref>.        </p>
    <p>
A 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_nurse_clinic">Nurse Clinic</xref>
 is an administrative arrangement enabling 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_patient">PATIENTS</xref>
 to see or be in contact with a 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_nurse">NURSE</xref>
 for assessment, treatment, advice and/or counselling. 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_nurse_clinic">Nurse Clinics</xref>
 include clinics where 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_nurse">NURSES</xref>
 have their own list of 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_patient">PATIENTS</xref>
 who are not expected to see or be in contact with a doctor even though 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_patient">PATIENTS</xref>
 may be referred to a doctor by the 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_nurse">NURSE</xref>
 and seen or be in contact during the same attendance or contact. Note that this excludes 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_patient">PATIENTS</xref>
 attending or in contact with a 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_consultant_clinic">Consultant Clinic</xref>
 or a 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_midwife_clinic">Midwife Clinic</xref>. It also excludes 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_sexual_and_reproductive_health_clinic">Sexual and Reproductive Health Clinics</xref>. 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_nurse_clinic">Nurse Clinics</xref>
 may run in adjacent, concurrent sessions to 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_consultant_clinic_session">Consultant Clinic Sessions</xref>.        </p>
